\sqrt{\left(\dfrac{x-1}{2x}\right)^2 - \dfrac{y}{x}} = \dfrac{1}{2x} \sqrt{(x-1)^2 -4xy}
x>0
 \begin{align*} \sqrt{\left(\dfrac{x-1}{2x}\right)^2 - \dfrac{y}{x}} &= \sqrt{\dfrac{(x-1)^2}{(2x)^2} - \dfrac{y}{x} \cdot \dfrac{4x}{4x}} \\ &= \sqrt{\dfrac{(x-1)^2}{(2x)^2} - \dfrac{4xy}{4x^2}} \\ &= \sqrt{\dfrac{(x-1)^2}{(2x)^2} - \dfrac{4xy}{(2x)^2}} \\ &= \sqrt{\dfrac{(x-1)^2-4xy}{(2x)^2}} \\ &= \sqrt{\dfrac{1}{(2x)^2} \cdot \left( (x-1)^2-4xy \right)} \\ &= \sqrt{\left(\dfrac{1}{2x}\right)^2 \left((x-1)^2 -4xy\right)} \\ &= \sqrt{\left(\dfrac{1}{2x}\right)^2}\cdot \sqrt{(x-1)^2 -4xy} \\ &= \dfrac{1}{2x} \sqrt{(x-1)^2 -4xy} \end{align*} 
\sqrt{\left(\dfrac{x-1}{2x}\right)^2 - \dfrac{y}{x}} = \dfrac{1}{2|x|} \sqrt{(x-1)^2 -4xy}
x
\sqrt{\left(\dfrac{x-1}{2x}\right)^2 - \dfrac{y}{x}}=\sqrt{\dfrac{(x-1)^2}{4x^2} - \dfrac{y}{x}}=\sqrt{\dfrac{(x-1)^2-4xy}{4x^2}}=\dfrac{1}{2|x|} \sqrt{(x-1)^2 -4xy}
